John Compton (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Compton_(actor) 0 John Compton (June 21, 1923 – May 12, 2015) was an American actor. He starred in the television series The D.A.'s Man which aired in 1959. He appeared in the films Mildred Pierce, Cheyenne, Jesse James Rides Again, Oh! Susanna, Thunder Over Arizona and Spoilers of the Forest, among others. He died of natural causes on May 12, 2015, in Los Angeles, California at age 91.
